title: Tuesday Post Show (09-27-22)

description:
Bobby is still recovering from the weekend in Vegas and Lunchbox said he had to put himself on vocal rest. We talk about our favorite games to play in Vegas.  Bobby shares how much he won in Vegas. We share the rest of the Vegas stories we didn’t get to.
